commit_message:
Add policy cooldown support

This patch provides policy cooldown support. The following works
were done in this patch:

1. Cooldown check and reset methods were implemented in policy base
   module;
2. Add policy cooldown examination with the following logic:
    - cooldown check will be done before invoking policy.pre_op() if
      policy targets on 'BEFORE' stage of current action;
    - cooldown check will be done before invoking policy.post_op() if
      policy targets on 'AFTER' stage of current action;
    - cooldown check will be skipped if policy doesn't target to any
      stage of current action;
3. Add policy cooldown reset with the following logic:
    - cooldown timestamp will be reset when action execution finished
      if policy targets on 'BEFORE' or 'AFTER' stage of current action;
    - cooldown timestamp will not be updated if policy doesn't target
      to any stage of current action;

